            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-861e4962-be27-44a8-8c8b-c5e6408dd19d">
                The President of the Board of Trade (Sir Stafford Cripps)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-861e4962-be27-44a8-8c8b-c5e6408dd19d" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
