<p class="">Surely, that dealt with the Paris Conference?</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
                        <a href="#contribution-9839767e-362d-44fb-ba95-c1a78c4fa10a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-to-contribution-mobile link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
