            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-eabb0d02-8d05-4397-9c3f-73d1b7a57939">
                Mr. Messer  (Tottenham, South)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-eabb0d02-8d05-4397-9c3f-73d1b7a57939" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
