ie, J H. (Galloway)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bowen, R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gates, Maj E. E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Maclay, Hon. J. S.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bower, N.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>George, Maj. Rt Hn. G. Lloyd (P'ke)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Macmillan, Rt. Hon. Harold (Bromley)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Boyd-Carpenter, J. A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>George, Lady M. Lloyd (Anglesey)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Macpherson, N. (Dumfries)</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bracken, Rt. Hon. Brendan</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Glyn, Sir R.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Maitland, Comdr. J. W.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Bromley-Davenport, Lt.-Col W</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gomme-Duncan, Col. A</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Manningham-Buller, R. E</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Butcher, H. W.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Gridley, Sir A.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Marlowe, A. A. H</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Butler, Rt. Hon. R. A. (S'flr'n W'Id'n)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Grimston, R. V.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Marples, A E.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Byers, Frank</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hannon, Sir P. (Moseley)</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Marsden, Capt. A.</td></p><p class="Division">  </tr></p><p class="Division">  <tr></p><p class="Division"> <td>Carson, E.</td></p><p class="Division"> <td>Hare, Hon. J. H. (Woodbridge)</td></p><p c